---
description: "Deployment guidelines for determining the platform and handling Cloudflare Pages."
globs:
  - "nuxt.config.ts"
alwaysApply: true
---

- **Cloudflare Pages:**
  Only apps that extend `@serp/utils-cloudflare-pages` in their nuxt.config.ts are deployed to Cloudflare Pages.

- **Other Platforms:**
  Apps not using utils-cloudflare-pages may use alternative deployment platforms.

- **Determine Platform:**
  Check nuxt.config.ts to see if it extends `@serp/utils-cloudflare-pages`.
